| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3796 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5aae9971-317f-58c6-97ad-39aa35d04ee2"
